---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="美國直送商品 - Black Living 黑哥家居"
  description="美國原裝進口床墊與寢具用品，品質保證直送到府"
>
  <main class='container mx-auto px-4 py-8'>
    <div class='text-center mb-12'>
      <h1 class='text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4'>美國品牌代購專區</h1>
      <p class='text-xl text-gray-600'>敬請期待更多美國原裝進口商品</p>
    </div>

    <div class='text-center py-20'>
      <div class='max-w-md mx-auto'>
        <h2 class='text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4'>即將推出</h2>
        <p class='text-gray-600 mb-8'>我們正在為您精選更多優質的美國品牌商品</p>
        <a
          href='/appointment'
          class='inline-block bg-black text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors'
        >
          立即預約諮詢
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
